 aku i na pilikia o ka honua holo'okoa, e ha'awi mai i ka mana nui hekau aku ka ˇale o ko kakou na'au lawelawe e kau aku i ka Moana PakÔpika, e pae aku i na kapa kai o ka Hikina a hiki i ke Komohana.","category":"General Prayers","order_in_cat":5},{"phelps":"BH11209","text":"## He Pule Koi Pˆkole\n* Short Obligatory Prayer\n\nˇO wau ko'u ho'ike, e ku'u Akua, nau i hana mai ia'u e ho'omaopopo ia ˇOe a'e ho'omana ia ˇOe. Ke ho'oia'i'o nei wau i kÎia manawa, i ko'u ikaika ˇole a me Kou mana ikaika, i ku'u ˇilihune a i Kou waiwai palena ˇole.\n\nˇA'ole mea e a'e, ˇO ˇOe wale no e ku'u Akua, he Kokua kokoke i ka wa popilikia, ˇO ˇOe ka mea apau, nau i hana na mea apau.","name":"Short Obligatory Prayer","category":"He Pule Koi Pˆkole","cat_order":1,"order_in_cat":1,"translations":[{"language":"af","lang_name":"Afrikaans"},{"language":"sq","lang_name":"Albanian"},{"language":"am","lang_name":"Amharic"},{"language":"ar","lang_name":"Arabic"},{"language":"ar-translit","lang_name":"Arabic (Latin)"},{"language":"az","lang_name":"Azerbaijani"},{"language":"be","lang_name":"Belarusian"},{"language":"bi","lang_name":"Bislama"},{"language":"bs","lang_name":"Bosnian"},{"language":"bg","lang_name":"Bulgarian"},{"language":"ca","lang_name":"Catalan"},{"language":"km","lang_name":"Central Khmer"},{"language":"ny","lang_name":"Chichewa"},{"language":"chn","lang_name":"Chinook Jargon"},{"language":"co","lang_name":"Corsican"},{"language":"cr","lang_name":"Cree"},{"language":"dak","lang_name":"Dakota"},{"language":"da","lang_name":"Danish"},{"language":"nl","lang_name":"Dutch"},{"language":"en","lang_name":"English"},{"language":"eo","lang_name":"Esperanto"},{"language":"fj","lang_name":"Fijian"},{"language":"fi","lang_name":"Finnish"},{"language":"fr","lang_name":"French"},{"language":"lg","lang_name":"Ganda"},{"language":"de","lang_name":"German"},{"language":"el","lang_name":"Greek"},{"language":"ht","lang_name":"Haitian Creole"},{"language":"hur","lang_name":"Halkomelem"},{"language"